00:01:17,360 --> 00:01:21,195
What's the first thing you think of
when you hear the word sulphur?

13
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:24,680
The benediction
of Our Lady Margaret?

14
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:28,436
Hydro-sulphic chlorination
of tetrametazine?

15
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:31,434
Or perhaps you think
of other things.

16
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:38,476
But think again, because sulphur,

17
00:01:38,640 --> 00:01:41,394
valency 16, atomic weight 32,

18
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:44,917
Citadel 5 1 5 7 000,

19
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:49,120
is one of the building blocks
of life itself.

20
