the humble match-head.

63
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,592
Peter Jackmond

64
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:24,992
is the Managing Director
of Lightning Decision Matches.

65
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:27,197
In an average year,

66
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:30,876
