40 tons of sulphur.

67
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:35,592
This translates into approximately
21 million individual matches.

68
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:38,434
Since the company was formed,

69
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:43,391
