280 thousand matches.

70
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:46,632
If we continue
at the current rate of production,

71
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:49,076
by the year 3500,

72
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:54,952
we'll have made 900 thousand,
billion, billion, billion, billion,

73
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:57,874
billion, billion matches.

74
